name: Chronicles of the Starborn
description: Embark on a cosmic odyssey with the Yu-Gi-Oh! CCG expansion, Chronicles of the Starborn, where interstellar warriors, astral machines, and luminous destinies collide to shape the fate of the galaxy.

name: Phantom Parade
description: Step into the eerie and enchanting world of the Yu-Gi-Oh! CCG Halloween special booster set, Phantom Parade, where ghostly apparitions and vampiric forces converge to rewrite the rules of dueling.

name: Dawn of the Elements
description: Make waves and ignite the meta with the Yu-Gi-Oh! TRADING CCG core booster set, Dawn of the Elements, bursting with dynamic new archetypes like Aquamarine, Chrono, Phlogiston, and more!

name: Cosmic Origins
description: Jump into the epic clash for the galaxy with the Yu-Gi-Oh! CCG core booster set, Cosmic Origins, packed with powerful support cards, standout singles, and the thrilling dawn of the Eldora Saga!

name: Tainted Tales
description: Unleash a saga of cosmic chaos and strategic mastery with the Yu-Gi-Oh! CCG core booster set, Tainted Tales, where archetypes like Stain and Stellaer rewrite the battlefield
